column10: The Apache Gora™ open source framework provides an in-memory data model and persistence for big data. Gora supports persisting to column stores, key value stores, document stores, distributed in-memory key/value stores, in-memory data grids, in-memory caches, distributed multi-model stores, and hybrid in-memory architectures. Gora also enables analysis of data with extensive Apache Hadoop MapReduce and Apache Spark support.
